@startuml
' Use template styling (monochrome, etc.)
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title US2.2.10: View the Status of Vessel Visit Notifications - System Sequence Diagram (SSD)

autonumber
actor "Shipping Agent Representative" as Agent
participant ":System" as System

activate Agent

'--- View All Notifications ---
Agent -> System : requests list of all Vessel Visit Notifications\n(submitted by self or same organization)
activate System
System --> Agent : retrieves and returns notifications with statuses\n(In Progress, Pending, Approved, Rejected)
deactivate System

'--- Filter by Criteria ---
... Agent applies filters ...
Agent -> System : searches notifications by (vessel, status, representative, time)
activate System
System --> Agent : returns matching filtered notification records
deactivate System

deactivate Agent
@enduml
